Readme LinuxKernel/Scripts/Applications
---------------------------------------

Sayulita Voice Project HAM Radio Repeater

Architecture
------------

Report Infrastructure
|-log
|-voice
|-telemetry
|-twitter
|-cw

Hardware Infrastructure
|-radio
|-tnc
|-internet
|-gps
|-sensors
  |-temperature

Interface Infrastructure
|-serial
|-parallel
|-ethernet
|-wifi
|-i2c

Service Infraestructure
|-news
|-weather
|-sismic
|-events
|-location
|-date
|-time
|-alarm
|-learning

Usages
|-High Altitude Ballon Flight Controller
|-Repeater Assistant

Details
|-Report Infraestructure
  can report through file, voice, telemetry and twitter
  offers 3 level of information: none, minimum, maximum
